    <div class="prose">
      <p>When the documented steps don&rsquo;t hold, the cause is usually past the surface &mdash; a damaged network-data (.ND) file, a multi-version conflict, a firewall rule that resets, or genuine company-file integrity damage. A Certified ProAdvisor with active Desktop and Enterprise certifications diagnoses the actual root cause, fixes it against a written scope, and verifies multi-user access is stable before closing. Independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s software support.</p>
